    <string name="terms_title">Terms of Service &amp; Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="terms_content">1. Service Declaration\nThis app is a purely local menstrual tracking tool. All functions run locally on the device with no network interaction. We do not collect, upload, or share any of your personal data.\n\n2. User Responsibility\nYou are responsible for the accuracy of the physiological data entered. The menstrual predictions, ovulation calculations, and pain analysis provided by this app are for reference only and do not constitute medical diagnosis. If you have health concerns, please consult a professional doctor.</string>
    <string name="privacy_title">Privacy Policy</string>
    <string name="privacy_content">1. Core Principle: Data Localization\nAll your menstrual, symptom, and temperature data is stored only in the encrypted database on your phone. The app has no network permissions, fundamentally preventing data leakage.\n\n2. Information Collected\nWe only process information you manually enter locally.</string>
